summary: CHECK ENGINE LIGHT CAME ON WITH CODE FOR CYLINDER MISFIRE. DID RESEARCH ONLINE WHAT PROBLEM MIGHT BE AND SEEN THOUSANDS OF COMPLAINTS WITH EXACT SAME ISSUE.
